Class Market

java.lang.Object
market.markets.Market
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Dealer, Searchable
Direct Known Subclasses:
MarketWithIndices
public class Market extends Object implements Searchable, Dealer, Serializable
Market is a container for Assets that can be bought on it. Market add additional cost to each transaction performed on it
